snippet.title: Road 96 - Release Date Announcement - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Road 96 is a procedural narrative game with survival elements in which players must escape a country on the brink of collapse. Discover atypical protagonists in a declining world through your path, thousands of miles away in the mountains. No one's road is the same in Road 96. 

Coming to Nintendo Switch on August 16th, 2021! https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/road-96-switch/
